{"tid":216612,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"最強免費通識精讀班．第三堂（數據趨勢題）","createTime":"2017-04-25T10:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T11:26:52.000Z","uid":101377,"like":8,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"816c2a8d5d130a459da660da35fe6a313a22cfa6","tid":216612,"uid":101377,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:08:28.000Z","msg":"最強免費通識精讀班．第三堂（數據趨勢題）<br />\n<br />\n第三堂，教授數據趨勢題的絕技<br />\n各類性質的資料，唔難唔做<br />\n<br />\n我決定上載更多更多更多免費的教學影片供同學觀看<br />\n課程教授的題型亦已就2018DSE的出題趨勢作出適當調整<br />\n內容將一堂比一堂精彩及豐富<br />\n各種題型及資料，與你逐一擊破<br />\n保證最強，最實用<br />\n<br />\n第三堂的影片網址：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xA4NjOh2foQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxA4NjOh2foQ&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5fiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=770480ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xA4NjOh2foQ</a><br />\n<br />\nIG：i.liberal.studies<br />\nFB：<a href=\"http://facebook.com/i.liberal.studies\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fi.liberal.studies&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5fiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=afed1fa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">facebook.com/i.liberal.studies</a><br />\n同學可透過fb免費索取課堂的筆記<br />\n<br />\n保證你只要上完我的大考精讀班<br />\n通識科，根本不用補習<br />\n（需配合你平日於日校專心上課）"},{"pid":"8616c3897d124e6afe2db8733bc7332303792ac8","tid":216612,"uid":104088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:19:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"212217b3140ad9209c41d2b2b36d4ef38652eb04","tid":216612,"uid":101377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T14:09:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901e9077b53f0044b268146ef1047beff45315ca","tid":216612,"uid":62993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T14:16:06.000Z","msg":"你好啊馬神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cdc0999ffe4b1acf0c86dcff19764f166d933ac","tid":216612,"uid":37037,"like":0,"dislike"